description: Screenshots: http://imgcouch.com/image/1Tb4 IMDB: http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1839337/ Singer Jennifer Hudson takes a turn in the iconic red chair alongside Miley, Adam and Blake as they coach undiscovered hopefuls in this groundbreaking, Emmy Award-winning singing competition.
